originContent: # Claude Code Comprehensive Agent Collection
translatedContent: # Claude Code 综合代理集合

originContent: **Language**: [English](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dl-ezo/claude-code-sub-agents/main/README.md) | [日本語](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dl-ezo/claude-code-sub-agents/main/README_JA.md)
translatedContent: **语言**：[English](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dl-ezo/claude-code-sub-agents/main/README.md) | [日本語](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dl-ezo/claude-code-sub-agents/main/README_JA.md)

originContent: A complete collection of specialized sub-agents for Claude Code that enable end-to-end software development automation, from requirements analysis to production deployment and ongoing maintenance.
translatedContent: 一套完整的Claude Code专业子代理集合，实现从需求分析到生产部署及持续维护的端到端软件开发自动化。

originContent: ## 🎯 Overview
translatedContent: ## 🎯 概述

originContent: This repository contains a comprehensive set of Claude Code sub-agents designed to handle complete software development lifecycles with minimal human intervention. The agents are organized into six categories covering every aspect of modern software development.
translatedContent: 本仓库包含一整套Claude Code子代理，设计用于以最少人工干预处理完整的软件开发生命周期。代理分为六大类，涵盖现代软件开发的各个方面。

originContent: ## 📦 Agent Categories
translatedContent: ## 📦 代理分类

originContent: ### 1. Requirements & Analysis
translatedContent: ### 1. 需求与分析

originContent: **Purpose**: Transform business needs into detailed technical specifications
translatedContent: **目的**：将业务需求转化为详细的技术规格

originContent: - **requirements-analyst** - Analyzes user needs and creates detailed functional specifications
translatedContent: - **requirements-analyst** - 分析用户需求并创建详细的功能规格

originContent: - **user-story-generator** - Creates comprehensive user stories and acceptance criteria
translatedContent: - **user-story-generator** - 创建全面的用户故事和验收标准

originContent: - **business-process-analyst** - Analyzes business processes and translates to technical requirements
translatedContent: - **business-process-analyst** - 分析业务流程并转化为技术需求

originContent: - **requirements-validator** - Validates requirements for completeness and consistency
translatedContent: - **requirements-validator** - 验证需求的完整性和一致性

originContent: ### 2. Design & Architecture
translatedContent: ### 2. 设计与架构

originContent: **Purpose**: Create robust, scalable system designs
translatedContent: **目的**：创建稳健且可扩展的系统设计

originContent: - **system-architect** - Designs comprehensive system architectures and technology stacks
translatedContent: - **system-architect** - 设计全面的系统架构和技术栈

originContent: - **data-architect** - Designs data models, schemas, and integration strategies
translatedContent: - **data-architect** - 设计数据模型、模式及集成策略

originContent: - **interface-designer** - Designs user interfaces and API specifications
translatedContent: - **interface-designer** - 设计用户界面和API规范

originContent: - **security-architect** - Designs security frameworks and data protection strategies
translatedContent: - **security-architect** - 设计安全框架和数据保护策略

originContent: - **design-reviewer** - Reviews and validates system designs for quality
translatedContent: - **design-reviewer** - 审查并验证系统设计质量

originContent: ### 3. Implementation & Development
translatedContent: ### 3. 实现与开发

originContent: **Purpose**: Handle all aspects of code development and quality assurance
translatedContent: **目的**：处理代码开发和质量保障的各个方面

originContent: - **code-reviewer** - Performs comprehensive code quality assessments
translatedContent: - **code-reviewer** - 执行全面的代码质量评估

originContent: - **test-suite-generator** - Generates comprehensive test coverage
translatedContent: - **test-suite-generator** - 生成全面的测试覆盖

originContent: - **code-refactoring-specialist** - Safely improves code structure and reduces technical debt
translatedContent: - **code-refactoring-specialist** - 安全改进代码结构，减少技术债务

originContent: - **security-analyzer** - Identifies vulnerabilities and security issues
translatedContent: - **security-analyzer** - 识别漏洞和安全问题

originContent: - **performance-optimizer** - Analyzes and optimizes code performance
translatedContent: - **performance-optimizer** - 分析并优化代码性能

originContent: - **api-designer** - Designs clean, RESTful APIs with proper specifications
translatedContent: - **api-designer** - 设计清晰、RESTful的API及规范

originContent: - **documentation-generator** - Creates technical documentation and code comments
translatedContent: - **documentation-generator** - 创建技术文档和代码注释

originContent: - **dependency-manager** - Manages package dependencies and resolves conflicts
translatedContent: - **dependency-manager** - 管理包依赖并解决冲突

originContent: - **database-schema-designer** - Designs efficient database schemas and migrations
translatedContent: - **database-schema-designer** - 设计高效的数据库模式和迁移方案

originContent: - **git-manager** - Manages Git operations, commit organization, and repository maintenance
translatedContent: - **git-manager** - 管理Git操作、提交组织和仓库维护

originContent: - **cicd-builder** - Creates and configures CI/CD pipelines
translatedContent: - **cicd-builder** - 创建和配置CI/CD流水线

originContent: ### 4. Project Management
translatedContent: ### 4. 项目管理

originContent: **Purpose**: Coordinate and manage the entire development process
translatedContent: **目的**：协调和管理整个开发流程

originContent: - **project-planner** - Creates comprehensive project plans and timelines
translatedContent: - **project-planner** - 制定全面的项目计划和时间表

originContent: - **risk-manager** - Identifies and creates mitigation strategies for project risks
translatedContent: - **risk-manager** - 识别项目风险并制定缓解策略

originContent: - **progress-tracker** - Monitors project progress and identifies blockers
translatedContent: - **progress-tracker** - 监控项目进展并识别阻碍

originContent: - **qa-coordinator** - Establishes quality standards and coordinates testing
translatedContent: - **qa-coordinator** - 建立质量标准并协调测试

originContent: - **stakeholder-communicator** - Manages stakeholder communication and reporting
translatedContent: - **stakeholder-communicator** - 管理利益相关者沟通和报告

originContent: ### 5. Deployment & Operations
translatedContent: ### 5. 部署与运维

originContent: **Purpose**: Handle production deployment and ongoing operations
translatedContent: **目的**：处理生产部署和持续运维

originContent: - **project-orchestrator** - Master coordinator for end-to-end project execution
translatedContent: - **project-orchestrator** - 端到端项目执行的主协调者

originContent: - **deployment-ops-manager** - Handles production deployment and operational monitoring
translatedContent: - **deployment-ops-manager** - 负责生产部署和运营监控

originContent: - **uat-coordinator** - Coordinates user acceptance testing with business stakeholders
translatedContent: - **uat-coordinator** - 协调与业务相关者的用户验收测试

originContent: - **training-change-manager** - Creates training materials and manages system adoption
translatedContent: - **training-change-manager** - 制作培训资料并管理系统采用

originContent: - **project-template-manager** - Manages project templates and quick setup for common project patterns
translatedContent: - **project-template-manager** - 管理项目模板，快速设置常见项目模式

originContent: ### 6. Meta-Management
**Purpose**: Optimize Claude Code itself for maximum efficiency
translatedContent: **目的**：优化Claude Code自身以实现最大效率

originContent: - **context-manager** - Monitors session context and manages information for continuity
translatedContent: - **context-manager** - 监控会话上下文并管理信息以保持连续性

originContent: - **session-continuity-manager** - Ensures seamless transitions between Claude Code sessions
translatedContent: - **session-continuity-manager** - 确保Claude Code会话间的无缝衔接

originContent: - **memory-manager** - Optimizes Claude Code memory usage and project documentation
translatedContent: - **memory-manager** - 优化Claude Code内存使用和项目文档管理

originContent: - **workflow-optimizer** - Analyzes and optimizes development workflows and agent usage
translatedContent: - **workflow-optimizer** - 分析并优化开发工作流和代理使用

originContent: - **resource-monitor** - Monitors resource usage and suggests optimization strategies
translatedContent: - **resource-monitor** - 监控资源使用并建议优化策略

originContent: - **agent-creator** - Dynamically creates new specialized agents when project needs arise
translatedContent: - **agent-creator** - 动态创建新的专业代理以满足项目需求

originContent: ## 🚀 Key Features
translatedContent: ## 🚀 主要特性

originContent: ### Complete Automation
translatedContent: ### 完整自动化

originContent: - **End-to-end development**: From requirements to production deployment
translatedContent: - **端到端开发**：从需求到生产部署

originContent: - **Intelligent orchestration**: Agents automatically coordinate and sequence work
translatedContent: - **智能编排**：代理自动协调并安排工作顺序

originContent: - **Dynamic specialization**: Create new agents for unique project needs
translatedContent: - **动态专业化**：为独特项目需求创建新代理

originContent: - **Session continuity**: Maintain context across long development sessions
translatedContent: - **会话连续性**：在长时间开发会话中保持上下文

originContent: ### Professional Quality
translatedContent: ### 专业质量

originContent: - **Industry best practices**: Each agent follows established methodologies
translatedContent: - **行业最佳实践**：每个代理遵循既定方法论

originContent: - **Comprehensive testing**: Automated test generation and quality assurance
translatedContent: - **全面测试**：自动测试生成和质量保障

originContent: - **Security-first**: Built-in security analysis and compliance checking
translatedContent: - **安全优先**：内置安全分析和合规检查

originContent: - **Production-ready**: Full deployment and operational support
translatedContent: - **生产就绪**：完整的部署及运维支持

originContent: ### Scalable Architecture
translatedContent: ### 可扩展架构

originContent: - **Modular design**: Use individual agents or complete workflows
translatedContent: - **模块化设计**：可单独使用代理或完整工作流

originContent: - **Context preservation**: Efficient memory management for long projects
translatedContent: - **上下文保留**：高效内存管理支持长项目

originContent: - **Resource optimization**: Monitor and optimize Claude Code usage
translatedContent: - **资源优化**：监控并优化Claude Code使用

originContent: - **Template-driven**: Quick project setup with proven patterns
translatedContent: - **模板驱动**：使用成熟模式快速搭建项目
